#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:4
msgid "Lamps"
msgstr "灯光"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:6
msgid ""
"Next to lighting from the background and any object with an emission shader,"
" lamps are another way to add light into the scene. The difference is that "
"they are not directly visible in the rendered image, and can be more easily "
"managed as objects of their own type."
msgstr ""
"除了背景光照和场景中具有自发光着色器的物体，灯光是为场景提供光照的另一种方法。不同的是，在渲染图中，它们并不是能直接可见的，而且也可以作为特有的物体属性进行管理。"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:14
msgid "Type"
msgstr "类型"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:17
msgid "Size"
msgstr "尺寸"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:17
msgid ""
"Size of the lamp in Blender Units; increasing this will result in softer "
"shadows and shading."
msgstr "灯光的尺寸，以blender单位计，值越大，则阴影和明暗过渡就会越柔和。"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:26
msgid "Cast Shadow"
msgstr "投射阴影"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:24
msgid ""
"By disabling this option, light from lamps will not be blocked by objects "
"in-between. This can speed up rendering by not having to trace rays to the "
"light source."
msgstr "禁用此选项，灯光发出的光线将不会被沿途的物体所遮挡。这会加快渲染速度，因为不必去对光源的光线进行追踪。"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:29
msgid "Point Lamp"
msgstr "点光灯"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:31
msgid ""
"Point lamps emit light equally in all directions. By setting the *Size* "
"larger than zero, they become spherical lamps, which give softer shadows and"
" shading. The strength of point lamps is specified in Watts."
msgstr ""
"点光的光线从某一点向各个方向均匀发出。将尺寸设置为正值的话，可以将其转变成球形光源，这会提高更加柔和的阴影及明暗过渡。点光灯的强度以瓦特为单位。"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:37
msgid "Spot Lamp"
msgstr "聚光灯"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:39
msgid ""
"Spot lamps emit light in a particular direction, inside a cone. By setting "
"the *Size* larger than zero, they can cast softer shadows and shading. The "
"size parameter defines the size of the cone, while the blend parameter can "
"soften the edges of the cone."
msgstr ""
"聚光灯会沿着特定方向在锥形范围内投射光线。如果将它的Size（尺寸）值设为正数，那么将会得到柔和的阴影和着色效果。Size（尺寸）参数定义了锥形区域的尺寸，而"
" blend（混合）参数可以调节锥形边缘的柔化效果。"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:46
msgid "Area Lamp"
msgstr "面光灯"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:48
msgid ""
"Area lamps emit light from a square or rectangular area with a Lambertian "
"distribution."
msgstr "面光是从一个正方形或长方形区域发光，采用Lambertian distribution（朗伯分布）方式。"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:62
msgid "Sun Lamp"
msgstr "日光灯"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:64
msgid ""
"Sun lamps emit light in a given direction. Their position is not taken into "
"account; they are always located outside of the scene, infinitely far away, "
"and will not result in any distance falloff."
msgstr "日光光源沿着某一指定的方向发光。其位置无关紧要，它们通常位于场景外部，距离无限远，并且不会产生任何的距离衰减效果。"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:68
msgid ""
"Because they are not located inside the scene, their strength uses different"
" units, and should typically be set to lower values than other lights."
msgstr "由于它们不在场景内部应用，因此使用了不同的强度单位，相对与其它种类光源而言，应被赋予相对较低的值。"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:51
msgid "Light Portals"
msgstr "日光入口"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:53
msgid ""
"Area lamps can also function as light portals to help sample the environment"
" light, and significantly reduce noise in interior scenes. Note that "
"rendering with portals is usually slower, but as it converges more quickly, "
"less samples are required."
msgstr ""
"面光灯可以当做日光入口来帮助对环境光的采样，可以极大的减少室内渲染的噪点。注意渲染带日光入口的场景的时候会慢一些，但是收敛（降噪点）是非常快的，采样数要求也不高。"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:57
msgid ""
"Light portals work by enabling the Portal option, and placing areas lamps in"
" windows, door openings, and any place where light will enter the interior."
msgstr "开启入口选项后日光入口开始工作，把面光源放到窗口，开门出或者室内其他光能进来的地方。"

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:12
msgid ""
"Currently *Point*, *Spot*, *Area* and *Sun* lamps are supported. *Hemi* "
"lamps are not supported, and will be rendered as point and sun lamps "
"respectively, but they may start working in the future, so it's best not to "
"enable them to preserve compatibility."
msgstr ""
"目前支持Point（点光）、Area（面光）、Sun（日光）以及Spot（聚光）四种灯光类型。暂不支持hemi（半光）类型，并且将会分别作为点光和日光灯光进行渲染。不过，在将来会获得支持，所以，为了提高兼容性，最好先不要使用它们。"

